values: Anyone who wants to call me can...if you don't..taht is cool too...what ever works best for you! Love you all!

I am sorry for everything I have ever done! May, I am sorry I have been so hard on you, but the truth is, you are great, and I am so glad Margery has found someone so great. You have your flaws, like everyone else, and I am sorry that I was so mean! Margery, I don't know what I said that made you so mad at me, I am sorry. If you think I am two faced, then it must be true, because you know me very well, and may and john told me that as well! I know I am not always right, and I have stopped trying to be ever since you brought it up that one time a while back. I am sorry for the pain I have caused you as well. To Sarah, thanks for always being there, and never taking thinkgs I saw to heart...it makes it alot easier to know that you know I don't mean it. Amy, same to you, you are one of those people who have always been there. I hadn't talked to you since the middle of school, but choose you to call out of everyone, because I knew you'd be there, you always are. To reed, I am sorry for screwing you over, and what ever made you mad at me..I am truely sorry for! I know I have been a bitch, but I want to change...whether you want to be there to watch me is your choice. I know I have made some bad decisions in the past but I am really sorry for the pain I have caused! I know a simple sorry doesn't make up for a lot but, I hope someday you will let me show you, let me prove to you that I love you, always have, and always will! I hope everyone wont stay mad at me, because of what I have done! I don't mean to hurt anyone...as most of you know..I just try to help! I messed up real bad this time..and I am sorry to everyone I brought down in the process! Thank you to everyone for listening!

Reed,

Dude, you were dumb as fuck! You told may the one think I told you not to...what the hell! Giving me more stress, more drama that I have to sort out! And you know what else, yeah, I tell my friends shit...but in no way do I go in to detail. You told May WAY!!! too much...and he told bishop! That was so not even cool! That's fucked up as hell! Things got fucked up as hell really fast!

May,

I got  on and my name was for margery, who ever wrote that shit about john, and some people from my past. None of that had to do with you, and you got mad! You weren't the only one accused. So was Reed, Bishop, and even sarah. Infact, I think John might have even thought I did it. I didn't do shit..you just got all pissed off! I don't know why...i didn't strait up accuse you...i just asked if reed thought it was you! That is it...nothin wrong in that!

Margery: Saturday I got on and had my screen anem somthing about how some peoplewere never my friends. I told you why and who I was talking about and all's you said  was, "you did screw reed over pretty bad". That is why you were part of my screen name. You got in my business when you didn't need to be! You know, I don't mind so much you got up in my shit, its that you should have been a suportive best friend!

Hey, 

What is up ya'lls! Dude, someone keeps getting on Johns shit and being gay! Damn, I only know of one person who uses FAG and BUHLER BITCHES in the same sentences...and I think everyone can agree on who we think it is! My god, that is so gay that someone can say that, what the hell is the point! But, what ever floats your boat! I just hope no one I know is close to that person because if it is who I think it is...they are about to get fucked up!

Leave our men at home...if not this thursday then sometime...seriously! we have like never had all of us go out...just sometime when all of us have off...go and chill! Yeah, just sometime! OK, I have some more to say! I am so confused! Why are all of us fighting with Amy? We all have been friends for at least 3 or 4 years and all the sudden a little fight has us talkin shit and stuff! Amy, you were all talkin shit, and I did go tell John and Margery and the reason I didn't say anything is because I am trying to teach my self to keep my mouth shut! You know I need to do that! But yeah, we have been friends for ever and now we act like we hate each other over some guy shit! We all have promised not to do that...and this shit is stupid. I don't even know why we are fighting. We sat there and tried to help her by telling her so she wouldn't waste anymore of her life, and then she gets mad when we didn't do shit except relay on the message we had heard to help a friend! Where is the wrong in that! I don't know! But if someone could please tell my why we are all fighting!

Damn girl. I heard you said that you didn't want people to take the things you said personal. How could you not take "Fuck everyone" personal. That's just not something you don't take personal. And how John was just trying to act cool! Number one, no one was around, and two, if he was just trying to be cool, then the rest of us were too! We just try to be cool for each other...yeah, thats right. And how do you not take something personal when they say your name. Amy your stupid, but don't take it personal!

I am in a good mood today and I don't know why. It has been a horrible day. I woke up to my mom screeming at me telling me to clean the basement. Then she said I could help chloie move tonight (justin's mom) and I was mad. I was trying to get out of the house and forgot all kinds of things. My belt, my bookbag, underwear, lol, and I didn't brush my teeth. I got to school and rememberd I had to read 3 chaps in english, I had a worksheet and an assignment in Geometry with a quiz and a biology test. I didn't get to study or do any of my home work in the 3 most important classes. Grr. Then in english I was sitting there and got THREE pink slips. One for leaving my disc man on the bus and needed to come and get it. One for having 7 tardies, and one for getting an eighth on. But, I am still in a good mood.

I have been really moody latly and that is because everyday I am either sick of everyone or it seems like everyone is sick of me. I have been trying to avoid people and shit. But today I am just really happy. Sorry I have been snappy, I guess I can't help it. Latly if someone is mean to me, I am mean to them for like a week. Margery, If your track meet is at home on friday, I will come! Since I have a friday I will be able to come when I get out. Maybe I can get reed to come and pick me up and maybe you too! 

This weekend is my birthday and I have to spend friday night at school in a class room, then I have to stay at home on satuday because I am grounded. Reed promised me that I would have a good "sweet sixteen" but that was a lie! Oh well, I knew it wasn't going to happen anyways. I guess that is what me and Margery have in commom, no one care enough to do somthing special for us. But, hey! That is ok, I didn't do anything for anyone else.

This last weekend really stunk. I went out of town to KC with Reed and it totally blew. He pissed me off. I took him up there to get him away from his house, and to spend some time with him. I just wanted to cuddle the whole way up there, and it seemed all he wanted to do was anything but that. When we got there, he decided to make buddy buddy with landon. Everytime I would ask if he wanted to go do something he would stay in the house with landon or sit there and play on his damn cell phone. That night at the bond fire I would try to say somehting and he intrupted me twice with ok? or anyways! I was pissed. Then the next day he laughed at me when I said that I had to stay home on my birthday. He swears he didn't laugh, but I don't know. I guess I won't be able to take another guy on a family trip again. I thought he would make it better, but he made it that much worse. He asked me that night if I wanted to take a break and I just sat there. I don't because I will miss him, but I do because I don't want him to think that I will just forgve him for everything anymore. 

Yesterday at lunch jeff pissed me off really bad. He asked if me and reed would come over to some house to take pictures before rex and rossi left and I said reed would but I didn't know if I would. He automatically made the assumption that it was because I didn't want to be around those people, but that is wrong. I don't ahve a problem with any one of them...they are all tight no matter how much shit they talk. I didn't know if I would be there because I didn't know if me and reed would be tight on that day. But I think we will. 

Well, this is my week so far. and the rest of the week looks good, grounded, have my birthday, and that is about it. Oh, and how my mom bought my brother his firt two cars...well she says she didn't and it was monty. I said fine, even though she was lieing, and said I would buy it my self and she wouldn't be able to touch it, but she swears she can. If her name isn't on it, she can't touch it. From now on, I am going to get a job, get everything myself, and save some money, so I can move out. I don't know where I would go, but that is ok. I am planning on emancipation sometime in the next year to year in a half. Maybe reed and I could get somthing together! 

Ight, lata beaners! 

Cegan

REED! I am worring...so blow me! lol! I am so scared. You said you were growing up and weren't going to get mad at stupid shit anymore...well, I havn't grown up..and I still get mad. I am so afraid you will wanna kill me because I am immature. You know it is true. Grrr.!

I was cold because we didnt want to get my hair want so he got the water and I had to stand in the back..grr..that was shitty! But it was great!

OH, if he gets 50 brownie points..I have to strip for him! Grr...he isn't going to earn it..I will be sure of that! lol! He he, baby! You know I love you! 

Today is 11 months. Can you imagin being with someone that long...I used to not be able to believe it now I can't imagin my self without him. It is weird. My life at home sucks but when I leave that door it seems to be better, exspecially when I am leaving to see him! lol! That is enough of that sappy shit!

I talked to Stafford today..and he never said any of that shit. About sarah dancing. He said it the next day, but it was just a joke. I don't know who said he said that but now it is all cleared up, he didn't! So sarah, you gotta love him still! Well, you know what I mean! At least now you don't have a reason to hate him! So you can at least talk to him as a friend! Yeah! lol! 

Well, I think this is satisfactory for a day..two entries! Talk to you lata

She is almost completly out, thank god! lol! I guess Sarah had a pretty good time at prom. I guess because I hope he really didn't say that, because that would be jacked up. I think everyone had fun at one point or another. I don't know if I want to go next year, I think the prom will suck but I will want to go to after prom because BUHLERS is better than HUTCH's! ha ha!

They said they didn't have enough room for me to go...and they are taking 4 vehicals. I don't get it. There is only 8 people going. Two trailers, two trucks...two cars. that is two spots to sit for only 8 people...I don't know. It is weird...but that is ok! I am going to try to make reed's birthday good...I think he will like it. I am taking him out to eat at Carlo's O Kelly's...nothing special, but I think he will like it. THen I guess we will prolly just go somewhere...and do nothing. I wish I had money and lived in a different town so I could make it special. I wish I could do more for him. He has done so much for me!

That is what I pray for everynight, that everyone will be happy! I am sure it will happen someday soon, God works in misterious ways! lol! But yeah, that is that!

I got to go! Call me everyone!

Margery...you's is always on my friend list..my girl friend list at that..! lol! I know how it feels to think everyone hates you..I think it all the time..but I am starting to get over it and realize that everyone does love me and if they don't then there are plenty of other people out there..it has taken me almost a year to figure that out but I am dumb...so don't worry you will get it soon! I love you girl! It will pass. It is all good!
